![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-08T16-45-00-03-00/1680961046-416.jpg)The occupants forced the children to sing the Russian anthem, and Artem said.

![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-08T16-45-00-03-00/1680961045-669.jpg)“There were threats - we were frightened by a psychiatric hospital that they would give us there. We slept on the floor - there were no beds, pillows - some mattresses. The jackets were wailing, ”Artem said.

For her part, Anastasia said that they were forced to sing a Russian high -end week at a certain time, and for refusing were called thankless.

