As it was reported, the Verkhovna Rada adopted a law that introduces mechanism for the destroyed and damaged housing as a result of Russian aggression in Ukraine. Each citizen can submit an information message about the damaged property in electronic form - in "action", in paper - through CNAP. After verifying the documents, all data are added to the register of damaged property.

